**English:** Follow the development process in `docs/process/`. If this
repository has just been initialized, start with `docs/process/start-here.md`
and guide the user through Greenfield or Brownfield as a dialogue. Before
substantive work, read `mandatory-rules.md` and derive the tier from
`risk-tiers.md`. Tier 3+ requires a written plan under `.process-work/plans/`
before code.
